cu.explanation_en: Setting DRB ciphering to an invalid string value will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent secure communication setup.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PRACH DTX threshold to a negative value will cause invalid threshold handling and potential RACH procedure failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PRACH DTX 閾值設定為負值將導致無效的閾值處理，並可能導致 RACH 程序失敗。
